WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:02.272
Synced and corrected by Dragoniod for
www.addic7ed.com

00:02.297 --> 00:04.937
Arthur, did you see your sign?

00:04.962 --> 00:07.132
You're kidding me. They got me again?

00:07.157 --> 00:08.112
Got what?

00:08.137 --> 00:10.792
Oh, every spring, those senior girls

00:10.817 --> 00:14.417
from Blessed Heart, they mess
with my Superior Donuts sign.

00:14.526 --> 00:16.292
It's a classic prank.

00:16.294 --> 00:18.354
They unplug some letters
so it says "Super Nuts."

00:20.899 --> 00:23.733
"Super nuts" can also mean huge balls.

00:25.437 --> 00:26.970
Hilarious!

00:26.972 --> 00:28.851
Actually, it's a tradition.

00:28.876 --> 00:31.515
When I was a senior at
Blessed Heart, I did it.

00:31.540 --> 00:36.046
And by "did it," I mean started it.

00:36.048 --> 00:38.408
That's cute. Couple
schoolgirls do it, it's a prank.

00:38.433 --> 00:39.837
I do it, it's a felony.

00:41.720 --> 00:44.345
Did you guys see the sign?

00:44.370 --> 00:46.831
I know it's wrong, but I'm a
sucker for a good ball joke.

00:49.027 --> 00:51.327
Why do they always hit my shop, huh?

00:51.329 --> 00:54.397
"Buttons and Stuff" right
down the street, huh?

00:54.399 --> 00:56.259
You got it? Butt stuff.

00:59.276 --> 01:01.735
Every year he gets so upset.

01:01.790 --> 01:02.970
It's a harmless prank,

01:03.002 --> 01:04.367
like the time I passed out,

01:04.370 --> 01:06.370
and my brother wrote
"loser" on my forehead

01:06.372 --> 01:07.805
in permanent marker.

01:07.807 --> 01:09.440
I had just lost my job,

01:09.442 --> 01:11.855
so it really did a
number on me emotionally.

01:12.812 --> 01:15.279
But at the end of the day it was funny.

01:15.281 --> 01:17.014
To him.

01:17.016 --> 01:19.717
I miss my pranking days.

01:19.719 --> 01:22.634
Yesterday you filled
my holster with pudding.

01:23.923 --> 01:27.958
Yeah. I miss yesterday.

01:29.375 --> 01:29.994
Oh, Arthur,

01:29.996 --> 01:31.696
please don't tell me
you're about to climb that.

01:31.698 --> 01:33.631
- Why not?
- Because you're 75.

01:33.633 --> 01:35.466
You're pretty much made
of eggshells and nose hair.

01:35.468 --> 01:37.435
Oh, come on, what are you talking about?

01:37.437 --> 01:39.070
I got this. Here, take a look.

01:41.641 --> 01:43.708
Want to hop on my back, smart guy, huh?

01:43.710 --> 01:44.709
I could do this all day.

01:44.711 --> 01:46.177
Please stop.

01:46.179 --> 01:47.378
Your knees sound like someone

01:47.380 --> 01:48.813
biting into a Kit Kat.

01:50.682 --> 01:53.050
Arthur, just let Franco fix the sign.

01:53.052 --> 01:55.986
Yeah, it's why you hired one of them.

01:56.755 --> 01:59.690
What? A helper.

01:59.692 --> 02:01.659
Okay, stop being proud
and give me the ladder.

02:01.661 --> 02:03.294
- All right, all right, fine.
- Okay.

02:03.296 --> 02:04.595
Just take 'em out of the plugs.

02:04.597 --> 02:05.909
- Unplug plugs.
- Yeah, yeah, yeah...

02:05.934 --> 02:06.948
You'll figure it out
when you get up there.

02:06.973 --> 02:07.735
Yes, yes.

02:07.760 --> 02:09.333
There's no shame in accepting help.

02:09.335 --> 02:11.869
It doesn't mean you're
old, just that you're wiser.

02:11.871 --> 02:14.705
Which is another word for old.

02:14.707 --> 02:17.341
No, you wouldn't believe
how many emergency calls

02:17.343 --> 02:18.809
start out with someone
getting on a ladder

02:18.811 --> 02:21.078
to put up their Christmas lights.

02:23.348 --> 02:25.082
Do you remember that guy?

02:25.084 --> 02:27.017
He grabbed a strand of lights

02:27.019 --> 02:30.020
and got electrocuted
before hanging himself.

02:30.022 --> 02:33.157
His family is Jewish now.

02:34.360 --> 02:36.727
Franco!

02:37.696 --> 02:39.397
What happened?

02:39.399 --> 02:40.731
- Are you all right?
- You all right?

02:40.733 --> 02:43.334
I think I twisted my ankle.

02:43.336 --> 02:44.635
Oh, my God!

02:44.637 --> 02:48.305
"Superior Nuts."

02:48.307 --> 02:49.340
Which could also mean

02:49.342 --> 02:52.042
the finest testicles.

02:53.545 --> 02:57.124
He's hurt. I'm healing with laughter.

